s.t: FOR THIS THEME, I WANTED TO MAKE SOMETHINGTHAT WOULD ACCURATELY REPRESENT MY TASTESAND CHARACTERISTICS. HENCE WHY I CHOSE ACLEAN AND GEOMETRICAL THEME.THIS REFLECTS MY PREFERENCE FOR SYMMETRYAND CLEAN SHAPES/LINEWORK. I ALSO CHOSEONE OF MY FAVOURITE COLOUR COMBINATIONSTO FURTHER REPRESENT ME AS A DESIGNER.
